(151, 'Services', 'services', '', '<div class=\"clearfix\">\n</div><section id=\"inbanner\"><div class=\"container\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/Proxima360-service-banner2-1534x516.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid\"/><div class=\"solban-text\"><h1 id=\"ijv1\">Reshape Retail\n      </h1><p id=\"ic0f\">Gain a competitive edge through our unrivaled expertise in the retail industry\n      </p></div></div></section><br/><section id=\"ser-con\"><div class=\"container\"><p id=\"i56ly\"> Leverage our deep retail expertise along with our extensive experience in deploying core retail technology solutions\n    </p><div id=\"i4kuem\">From managing the customer experience to managing operations (logistics, manufacturing, distribution, storage, inventory) to managing support functions (financials), delivering services across the entire business value chain requires experienced and trusted resources. \n      <div><br/></div><div>Our approach combines technology and retail expertise to guide retail organizations through the retail roadmap blueprint, solution design, scalable and highly available infrastructure setup, solutions delivery, and support.\n      </div></div></div></section><section id=\"servi\"><div class=\"container py-2 mt-4 mb-4\"><!-- timeline item 1 --><div class=\"row\"><!-- timeline item 1 left dot --><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><!-- timeline item 1 event content --><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg1\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text d-flex\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Supply Chain\n                  </h4><p id=\"i86a3\">Consumer experiences live and die in the supply chain. Unlock the value of your data and get better supply chain planning results, faster.\n                  </p><p id=\"i01j4g\">With our deep supply-chain expertise together with core technology platforms including Oracle’s intelligent, cloud based SCM solutions, we stay on the leading edge by addressing tomorrow&#039;s supply chain needs today. \n                  </p><div class=\"col-md-6\"><br/><ul id=\"i7t24\"><li id=\"i3ch7\">Warehouse Management\n                      </li><li>Yard Management\n                      </li><li>Transportation Management\n                      </li><li>Store Fulfillment\n                      </li><li> Last Mile Delivery\n                      </li><li id=\"isib7\">Analytics &amp; Reporting\n                      </li></ul></div><a href=\"contact\" id=\"i0wej\">Supply Chain Management Bottlenecks? Contact Us <i draggable=\"true\" data-highlightable=\"1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"ip1tl\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center align-self-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/SupplyChain-proxima360-ul.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 2 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text d-flex\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Retail Finance\n                  </h4><p id=\"i86a3-2\">Retail finance plays a critical role in the success of a retail organization by ensuring smooth financial activities and processes in the day-to-day operations including making decisions related to inventory, pricing, and promotions, managing cash flow, and handling payments from customers.\n                  </p><p id=\"i01j4g-2\">Our in-house plug&amp;play retail stock and sales ledger provides visibility to your inventory and associated finances in real-time. The KPI&#039;s are aggregated at a week, month and half level for retail and cost accounting methods. Multiple currency, multiple set of books and multiple sales are supported. The feeder system can integrates with all ERP solutions in order to intake any inventory and sales transactions. \n                  </p><div class=\"col-md-6\"><br/><ul id=\"i7t24-2\"><li id=\"i3ch7-2\">Chart of Accounts Optimization\n                      </li><li id=\"iy6l34\">Sales Audit\n                      </li><li id=\"iqttfa\">Landed Cost Management\n                      </li><li id=\"imkgx1\">Sub-Ledger Setup\n                      </li><li id=\"ih8my2\">Invoice Matching &amp; Payments\n                      </li><li id=\"icjn21\">FP&amp;A Analytics\n                      </li></ul></div><a href=\"contact\" id=\"i0wej-2\">Get visibility of your inventory and sales transactions in real-time. Contact Us <i draggable=\"true\" data-highlightable=\"1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"i8qgr5\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center align-self-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/RetailFinance-Proxima360-OL.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 3 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text d-flex\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">eCommerce Operations\n                  </h4><p id=\"i86a3-3\">Consumer&#039;s expectations in today&#039;s world have changed. Consumers expect a lot more  from businesses and their expectations are not being formed by just what businesses do in the retail industry, but they are being shaped by some of the best on class companies like Amazon, Netflix, and Uber. \n                  </p><p id=\"i01j4g-3\">In the era of new normal where digital transformation is paving the way for industry wide adoption of eCommerce, our solutions are designed to provide consumers with delightful, effortless and a seamless experience. The result will be increased revenue per consumer and increased loyalty. \n                  </p><div><br/></div><div id=\"ifmxvo\">We are focused on creating end-to-end solutions that optimize the retail operational landscape and effectively address the gap between consumer expectation and their experience. \n                  </div><p>\n                  </p><div class=\"col-md-6\"><br/><ul id=\"i7t24-3\"><li id=\"i3ch7-3\">OMS Implementation\n                      </li><li id=\"i1t3c3\">Site Implementation\n                      </li><li id=\"icklv1\">Third-Party Integrations\n                      </li><li id=\"is89xq\">Payments and Taxes\n                      </li><li id=\"iuvbin\">Fraud and Return Management\n                      </li><li id=\"isib7-3\">Loyalty, Gifts Cards, Promotions &amp; Discounts\n                      </li></ul></div><a href=\"contact\" id=\"i0wej-3\">Unlock the value of your data by optimizing your OMS implementation. Contact Us <i draggable=\"true\" data-highlightable=\"1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"its9xt\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center align-self-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/eCommerce-proxima360-OL.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 4 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text d-flex\"><div id=\"iwfmax\" class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Merchandise Operations\n                  </h4><p id=\"i86a3-4\">Effective merchandise operations can help a retailer drive revenue, build customer loyalty, gain a competitive advantage, manage inventory levels, and make informed strategic decisions about the business.\n                  </p><p id=\"i01j4g-4\">Retailers need to transform their merchandise operations and make the connections between items, locations, and suppliers to track purchase orders, monitor income, manage replenishment settings, understand customer ordering, and aggregate transaction information into stock ledger reporting levels. \n                  </p><div><br/></div><div id=\"idto1t\">The professional services team at Proxima360 effectively leverages their retail experience and data analytics to solve the key challenge of effectively providing the right mix of merchandise to the warehouses and stores.\n                  </div><p>\n                  </p><div class=\"col-md-6\"><br/><ul id=\"i7t24-4\"><li id=\"i3ch7-4\">Assortment and Item Planning\n                      </li><li id=\"ionseh-2\">Oracle Merchandising Foundation Cloud Services\n                      </li><li id=\"ionseh\">Master Data Management\n                      </li><li id=\"ikcxgo\">PO and Trade Management\n                      </li><li id=\"ib6rff\">Inventory Management\n                      </li><li id=\"i3fwdf\">KPI Reporting\n                      </li></ul></div><a href=\"contact\" id=\"i0wej-4\">Getting the right mix of merchandise to the warehouse and stores? Contact Us <i draggable=\"true\" data-highlightable=\"1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"ie3mh7\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center align-self-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/MerchandiseOperations-proxima360-ul.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right0\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Store Operations\n                  </h4><p id=\"i86a3-5\">Addressing all five S&#039;s (Stock, Space, Staff, Standard and Systems) of retail operation could be a challenging task for any retailer.  \n                  </p><p id=\"i01j4g-5\">From efficient inventory management to the effective merchandising and streamlined checkout process, Proxima360 can assist in simplifying operations at the associate level so that they can use the best tools to transform the consumers; shopping experience.\n                  </p><div class=\"col-md-6\"><br/><ul id=\"i7t24-5\"><li id=\"i3ch7-5\">POS COnfigurations &amp; Upgrades\n                      </li><li id=\"is38vi\">Payment Gateway\n                      </li><li id=\"i15v0c\">Inventory Management\n                      </li><li id=\"ilaeqh\">Loyalty, Gift Card &amp; Discounts\n                      </li><li id=\"iyb36u\">Store Analytics Transformation\n                      </li><li id=\"isib7-5\">Payroll Integration and Analytics\n                      </li></ul></div><a href=\"contact\" id=\"i0wej-5\">Need to Optimize your store operations? Contact Us. <i draggable=\"true\" data-highlightable=\"1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" id=\"iv6vei\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center align-self-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/StoreOperations-proxima360-ul.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--></div><!--container--></section><section id=\"process\"><div class=\"container py-2 mt-4 mb-4\"><br/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"pro-bg\"><div class=\"col-md-10 offset-1\"><h1>Our Process\n          </h1><p id=\"ioktpo\">	At Proxima360, we believe that the key to success in the retail industry lies in a personalized approach to analyzing your current and future retail roadmap, as well as your data strategy, data channels, and sources and consumption of your data. By taking this approach, we can help you unlock the true value of your data, create a detailed understanding of consumers&#039; DNA, and empower you with timely data access for faster decision-making across the entire enterprise value chain. Our goal is to enable collaboration and ensure that you are equipped with the insights and tools needed to drive growth and profitability. Trust us to guide you on a smart way forward towards success in the retail industry.\n          </p></div></div></div><br/><br/><!-- timeline item 1 --><div class=\"row\"><!-- timeline item 1 left dot --><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">01</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><!-- timeline item 1 event content --><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg1\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Discovery &amp; Planning\n                  </h4><p id=\"idmukr\">At Proxima360, we put a strong emphasis on the discovery and planning phase to set clear goals and objectives. Discovery involves gathering requirements, analyzing the business needs, and understanding the problem domain. This phase helps in identifying the scope of the project and determining the feasibility of the solution. Planning involves defining the project timeline, identifying project milestones, and determining the resources required for the project. For us, a well-planned project ensures that our team is aware of the project&#039;s requirements, and the project is completed within the defined time and budget constraints. \n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 2 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">02</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Blueprinting \n                  </h4><p>Blueprinting is a crucial process that involves mapping out the existing and desired systems, processes, and workflows of a client&#039;s organization. This process helps us in identifying gaps and areas of improvement, create a plan for the implementation of new technology solutions, and ensure the successful adoption of these solutions. During the process, there is a continuous collaboration between Proxima360’s team and the client&#039;s stakeholders to ensure that the solution is tailored to the organization&#039;s specific needs. The resulting blueprint serves as a guide for the implementation process and ensures that the client&#039;s goals and objectives are met. \n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 3 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">03</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Solutions Design \n                  </h4><p>Based on a successful blueprinting session, the solution design process considers the technical feasibility, cost-effectiveness, and scalability of the proposed solution. The process includes defining the scope, conducting research, analyzing data, and proposing a solution that aligns with the client&#039;s business goals.\n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 4 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">04</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Solutions Implementation \n                  </h4><p> Software solution implementation, which is our key competency, involves translating the proposed solution design into a functional system that meets client&#039;s business needs to optimize their business processes and improve productivity. \n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><!-- timeline item 1 left dot --><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">05</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><!-- timeline item 1 event content --><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg1\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Support &amp; Maintenance\n                  </h4><p id=\"i22p8g\"> We provide training, support, and ongoing maintenance to ensure that the solution remains effective and continues to meet the client&#039;s needs. Our support services help ensure that the solution remains functional, secure, and up-to-date, and that the client&#039;s business operations continue smoothly.  We also provide regular updates and improvements to the system to keep it up-to-date with the latest technologies and trends. \n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--></div></section><br/><br/><section id=\"ban-img\"><div class=\"container\"><a href=\"contact\"> <img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/request-consult-1212x392-2.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/> </a></div></section><br/><br/>', '* { box-sizing: border-box; } body {margin: 0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;}body{margin:0;}*{box-sizing:border-box;