h 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Merchandise Operations\n                  </h4><p> Our streamlined process that gets your digital activations up and running. It starts with solution design and engineering, a site survey and\n                    verification audit, a curated technology\n                    package and system configuration, and is\n                    rounded out by the installation and activation.\n                  </p><a href=\"#\" id=\"i0wej-4\"> Case study <i draggable=\"true\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/MerchandiseOperations-proxima360-ul.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\"><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-check\">\n            </i></span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right0\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-6\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Store Operations\n                  </h4><p> POS Configurations &amp; Upgrades Payment Gateway Inventory Management Loyalty, Gift Cards &amp; Discounts Store Analytics Payroll Analytics.\n                  </p><a href=\"#\" id=\"i0wej-5\"> Case study <i draggable=\"true\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-arrow-circle-right\">\n                    </i> </a></div><div class=\"col-md-6 text-center\"><img src=\"https://proxima360.com/proxima_demo/uploads/gallery/StoreOperations-proxima360-ul.png\" class=\"img-fluid\"/></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--></div><!--container--></section><section id=\"process\"><div class=\"container py-2 mt-4 mb-4\"><br/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"pro-bg\"><div class=\"col-md-10 offset-1\"><h1>Our Process\n          </h1><p>	We take a personalized approach to understanding client pain points and helping them reach their digital transformation goals.\n          </p></div></div></div><br/><br/><!-- timeline item 1 --><div class=\"row\"><!-- timeline item 1 left dot --><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">01</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><!-- timeline item 1 event content --><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg1\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Exploration &amp; Discovery\n                  </h4><p>We start with a series of discovery meetings to better understand who you are as a brand, and what your digital transformation needs are. We’ll explore your goals, concerns, budget and more. This crucial phase ensures all parties are aligned on vision and objective.\n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 2 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">02</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card grey-bg\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Solution Design &amp; Engineering\n                  </h4><p>With a high-level understanding of your digital transformation goals, we can dive deeper into designing a custom-tailored solution. We’ll discuss locations, develop concepts, make recommendations, and talk pricing and timelines.\n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 3 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div><h5 class=\"m-2\"><span class=\"badge badge-pill bg-light border\">03</span></h5><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\"col\"> \n          </div></div></div><div class=\"col py-2\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-body\"><!--  <div class=\"float-right text-muted\">Mon, Jan 9th 2019 7:00 AM</div>--><div class=\"card-text\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-md-12\"><h4 class=\"card-title\">Strategy &amp; Planning\n                  </h4><p>Before your solution comes to life, we put the time in to ensure you hit the ground running. A dedicated account manager will coordinate with your in-house marketing team or AOR to align on content best practices and how to use our software to deploy media.\n                  </p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><!--/row--><!-- timeline item 4 --><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-auto text-center flex-column d-none d-sm-flex\"><div class=\"row h-50\"><div class=\"col border-right1\"> \n          </div><div class=\