(28, 'Clark Totten', 'uploads/team/Clark_Totten_250x250.jpg', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/clark-totten-387b776/', 'Director of Sales - North America', '', 'Clark brings a wealth of experience to Proxima360 given his 27+ years in the retail technology space.  Uniquely, Clark has spent time on both the vendor and client sides of the table having respectively worked for organizations such as Micros Retail, Island Pacific and The Walt Disney Company (Consumer Products).  Clark leverages a collaborative approach to his interactions resulting in positive results for all his clients.  Clark’s background also includes significant time spent in Professional Services further enabling his ability to see an issue from differing perspectives.  ', 'Inactive', NULL, 8, '2021-08-24', '0000-00-00', 0),
(29, 'Sunil Sood', 'uploads/team/sunil-sood-250x250.jpg', 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sunilksood/', 'EVP, Operations & HR', '', 'Sunil brings a 30+ year leadership experience helping businesses grow and scale their operations. Having worked in US, South East Asia, and India, Sunil has recruited and worked effectively with diverse workforce. Sunil has successfully developed, managed, and grown services businesses and have led large, complex projects, both internal and with global customers, with onshore and offshore teams. He has deep understanding of customer and employee experience management: of providing a delightful, effortless, and seamless experience to the customer and employees on one hand and growth, profitability, maximizing customer lifetime value for the organization on the other. Business operations improvement and process optimization is his biggest strength. ', 'Active', NULL, 6, '2021-11-10', '2021-12-14', 0);
